# Go Conventions

- Import path prefix: `github.com/SolaTyolo/herald/...`
- New providers: WASM under `plugins/wasm/<name>/` — see `docs/WASM_PROVIDERS.md`.
- Errors: wrap with context; return domain errors from services, not HTTP details.
- Tests: table-driven where sensible; use `t.Parallel()` when safe.
- After edits: run `go test ./...` for affected packages at minimum.
- Do not add comments that restate obvious code.
